subtrees and submodules together. Ugly stuff
Was constructed by:
git remote add prezto_remote https://github.com/sorin-ionescu/prezto.git
git fetch prezto_remote
git co -b prezto_branch prezto_remote/master
git submodule update --init --recursive
git co master
rm -rf modules
git read-tree --prefix=zsh/.zprezto -u prezto_branch
git ci


To checkout and update
git fetch 
git co -b prezto_branch origin/prezto_branch
git remote add prezto_remote https://github.com/sorin-ionescu/prezto.git
git pull
git co master
git merge --squash -s subtree --no-commit prezto_branch

Got it form https://git-scm.com/book/en/v1/Git-Tools-Subtree-Merging
